<template>
  <v-checkbox
    :value="value"
    @change="$emit('input', $event)"
    :label="label"
  ></v-checkbox>
  <v-checkbox v-model="isChecked" label="Check mejのテスト"></v-checkbox>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'AlldayCheck',
  props: ['value', 'label'],
  computed: {
    isChecked: {
      get() {
        return this.$store.state.isChecked;
      },
      set(value) {
        this.$store.commit('setChecked', value);
      },
    },
  },
};
</script>
